    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "find a way to release the pain... you make it sound like there's actually a way to do that. but it just feels like there's no point in pretending anymore. if that person is gone, what am i even supposed to do with this body? it's just a shell that keeps going even though nothing is left inside.",
